data.description: New updated Price!!   Gorgeous 4 Bedroom/2 Full Bathrooms with oversized lot with Built in Custom bar on the Lanai.  As you enter the home, you will find yourself in the spacious Dining room and Living room with tile flooring. The kitchen has beautiful granite countertops and stone backsplash. The Primary bedroom is located in the back of the home with a large walk in closet and Ensuite bathroom. The other three bedrooms are located on the other side of the home with a full bathroom. The huge Screened lanai is completely covered and has a unique custom made bar. The Garage has an epoxy flooring. This Beautiful home is located on a cul-de-sac which allows for a more private setting. Spencer Creek is in a great location close to Beaches, Amazon distribution center, I-75, Manatee viewing center. This home is a must see!!
